OL,3,CPort Lockroy: Inside the most remote
OL,4,Cmuseum in the world
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew delves into Britain's Antarctic
OL,8,Fpast at Port Lockroy
OL,10,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer
OL,11,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,13,FAround 800 miles away from the nearest
OL,14,Fbig city, hidden in the snow capped
OL,15,Fmountains sits an unassuming brown hut.
OL,17,FBehind its red doors is the most
OL,18,Fremote museum in the world.
OL,20,FThis is Port Lockroy.
