OL,3,CPort Lockroy: Inside the most remote
OL,4,Cmuseum in the world
OL,6,FIt is a former British military base -
OL,7,Festablished during World War II as
OL,8,Fpart of Operation Tarbarin.
OL,10,FThis was a secret operation to
OL,11,Festablish British presence in
OL,12,FAntarctica with the aims of gathering
OL,13,Fweather data and watching enemy ships
OL,14,Fin the Southern Ocean.
OL,16,FWhat started as a military operation
OL,17,Fsoon morphed into a scientific one as
OL,18,FPort Lockroy became the first
OL,19,Fpermanent British Research base on the
OL,20,Fcontinent.
