OL,3,CPort Lockroy: Inside the most remote
OL,4,Cmuseum in the world
OL,6,FNow Port Lockroy is open as a museum,
OL,7,Fshowcasing what life would have been
OL,8,Flike for the original explorers who
OL,9,Flived there.
OL,11,FSurprisingly, alongside all the
OL,12,Fpenguins, there is a post office. It
OL,13,Fis staffed by just a handful of people
OL,14,Fwho send a staggering 70,000 letters a
OL,15,Fyear.
